---


<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{PageTitle}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/about/">About</a>
        <a href="/blog/">Blog</a>
		<h1>{PageTitle}</h1>
        <h2> ... and my new Astro site!</h2>

        <p>
            I'm a software developer with a passion for building things. I'm a big fan of Astro and I'm excited to share my thoughts on it with you.
        </p>

        <p>
           This site is built with Astro. I'm using it to learn more about the framework and to share my thoughts on it with you.
           This site will update as I learn more about Astro and as I build more things with it.
        </p>

        <p> Here are few things about me: </p>
        <ul>
            <li>My Name is {identity.name}.</li>
            <li>I'm {identity.age} years old.</li>
            <li>My email is {identity.email}.</li>
            <li>I'm from {identity.country}.</li>
            <li>I'm a {identity.occupation}.</li>
            <li>Now I work at {identity.company}.</li>
            <li>My hobby is {identity.hobby[0]}, {identity.hobby[1]} and {identity.hobby[2]}.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>My skills are:</p>
        <ul>
            {skills.map(skill => <li>{skill}</li>)}
        </ul>

        {happy && <p> I am happy to be learning Astro!</p>}
        {finished && <p> I am finished with this site!</p>}
        {goal == 3 && <p> I am on goal {goal} days to finish this site!</p>}
	</body>
</html>
